Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:13.40,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming out of the tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:18.18,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! D'Arby is ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.70,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He's ahead by a car length!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:21.75,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,My speed will be doubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.74,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,I have won!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:25.54,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:29.82,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have less power left than me, D'Arby!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:32.70,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:39.93,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin's #28...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:45.35,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,spun and knocked D'Arby's car off the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.96,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And it was going at 850 kilometers per hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:50.37,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He's out of the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.03,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin's #28 safely landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.91,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:58.45,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,The one with less power goes flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:02.23,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you were wrong to think \Nthat losing power wouldn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:06.59,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't realize that I intentionally\Ndropped a length behind you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:08.30,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,so I could knock you off the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.50,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.50,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,It's you who didn't realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.18,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Losing power was all part of my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:23.02,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,I lost power on purpose so you'd \Npush my car off the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.57,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,This battle isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:29.77,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the direction my machine is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:32.02,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:42.97,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I-It flew over the curve and landed \Nfurther ahead on the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:44.24,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.34,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Normally, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:51.57,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Even at 850 kilometers per hour, once you're\Noff the course, you crash into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:54.46,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,You could never reach the\Nnext part of the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:58.72,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,But Kakyoin, if you were to slam into me,\Nit would become possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.47,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,I just needed you to send me flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:07.30,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,It was all part of my plan to reduce\Nmy power, then have you hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:08.98,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:12.73,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we continue the race, Kakyoin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.59,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't admit defeat, Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:24.83,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.36,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,I now hold his soul in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.92,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,He has just admitted defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:36.13,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,He admitted within his heart that \Nit was pointless to continue this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:43.80,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,But Kakyoin, you are the first \Nto ever make me sweat like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:56.07,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,This doll is now an especially\Nvaluable part of my collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.68,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,He is the first opponent to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:01.82,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,overcome his fears and not make any mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,due to mental weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.75,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:15.24,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,I shall treasure it,\Nand take very good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:18.42,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:23.29,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to warn you against \Nattacking me in retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.11,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,No, not just attacking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:30.11,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to slip on a banana \Npeel and hit my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:32.62,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,or choke on a piece of gum,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:37.69,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,or die of a heart attack from the bang \Nof an inflated popcorn bag being popped,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.70,JoJo-main,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin's soul would pass on\Nto the realm beyond this life.
